OL,4,CHydebank Wood Secure College and
OL,5,CFemale Prison
OL,7,FTwo prisons at one south Belfast site,
OL,8,Fwhich independent reports once
OL,9,Flabelled "not good enough", have now
OL,10,Fscored top marks in their most recent
OL,11,Funannounced investigations.
OL,13,FIn 2013, Hydebank Wood Secure College
OL,14,Fand Women's Prison were deemed to be
OL,15,Fon a "downward spiral", and "not
OL,16,Fhelping" inmates rehabilitate.
