OL,7,FNow though, inspectors have found
OL,8,Foutcomes for prisoners in both prisons
OL,9,Fwere 'good' against the four healthy
OL,10,Fprison tests of 'safety', 'respect',
OL,11,F'purposeful activity' and 'preparation
OL,12,Ffor release'.
OL,14,FThese are the highest possible scores.
