OL,3,CPositive reports for once failing
OL,4,CHydebank Wood Secure College and
OL,5,CFemale Prison
OL,7,FThere were still areas for improvement
OL,8,F- inspectors found that too many
OL,9,Finmates were missing planned hospital
OL,10,Fappointments. It was also noted that
OL,11,Fadult safeguarding arrangements "were
OL,12,Fnot fully effective", and "the
OL,13,Finvestigation of safeguarding
OL,14,Fincidents and serious complaints was
OL,15,Fnot sufficiently robust."
OL,17,FUTV was granted access to Hydebank
OL,18,Falong with other media outlets to film
OL,19,Fand conduct interviews in relation to
OL,20,Fthe findings of these reports.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
