OL,4,CHydebank Wood Secure College and
OL,5,CFemale Prison
OL,7,FThe tour included the busy beauty
OL,8,Fsalon, barber shop and mechanic lab
OL,9,Fwhere inmates study for courses with
OL,10,FBelfast Met.
OL,12,FThere were also filming opportunities
OL,13,Finside some cells, with the therapy
OL,14,Fdog Milo, inside the library and in a
OL,15,Frecreation room where some more
OL,16,Fvulnerable women were having tea and
OL,17,Fbuilding puzzles.
OL,19,FJustice Minister Naomi Long was in
OL,20,Fattendance.
