OL,7,FThe minister said she understands that
OL,8,Fsome viewers may feel prison doesn't
OL,9,Flook "awful" enough given that the
OL,10,Fprison houses criminals including
OL,11,Fconvicted murdered, but explained why
OL,12,Fit is important that they focus on
OL,13,Frehabilitation and opportunity for
OL,14,Fprisoners.
OL,16,FThese results come as the prison
OL,17,Fservice continues to feel the effects
OL,18,Fof a justice system under pressure.
